examples.en: He waited for the coincidence of the target and the cross hairs.
Treat his grey hairs with reverence.
There are dog hairs all over my coat.
A raw breeze whiffing about his grey hairs.
The cat has left white hairs all over the sofa.
The hairs turn white, become stumpy and brittle.
He heard a scream and the hairs on the back of his neck began to lift.
When the weather turns hot we help the dog to keep cool by combing out his loose hairs.
